{
  "texts": [
    "The basis of the study was a randomly selected 40 Virology MCQs, used for testing of medical students during the period 2017-2022.",
    "The MCQs were fully designed by the rst author (M.S.",
    "), with a PhD degree in Clinical Virology.",
    "The MCQs were original, without any copyright issues.The MCQs were classi ed based on the revised Bloom's taxonomy into two cognitive levels: higher involving 20 \"Remember\" and \"Understand\" MCQs; and lower involving 20 \"Apply\" and \"Analyze\" MCQs classi ed based on a consensus between the rst and senior authors.",
    "The MCQs were translated into Arabic by the rst author and back translated into English by the senior author, both bilingual in English and Arabic.The study was approved by the institutional review board (IRB) at the Faculty of Pharmacy -Applied Science Private University (reference number: 2024-PHA-5)."
  ]
}